<BaseLayout title="About" description="What the Bangpoundulary is and why it has paperwork.">
  <section class="official-card about-page">
    <p class="eyebrow">Institutional background</p>
    <h1>About the Bangpoundulary</h1>
    <p>The Bangpoundulary is the public dictionary of Wombology, a discipline devoted to word-combos that become something stranger than their roots intended.</p>
    <p>It began in Discord, acquired case law, developed rival institutes, gained CI, and now exists as a searchable public record because the bit crossed the infrastructure event horizon.</p>
    <p>The site is generated from Markdown entries in the public GitHub repo. Each entry preserves roots, status, sacrifice analysis, source provenance, and, when available, original corpus blocks.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
